                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271025-211-victim1084 t18271025-211-viclabel1217"></join> - the prisoner came and lodged at my house on the 8th of October; he was going out at seven o'clock in the morning, and seeming rather bulky, I called to my wife - she missed the sheets; I went out and took him with one round his body, and the other in his hat - he said he had come from Norwich.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. Q. Had I not my hat in my hand? A. Yes.</p>
